  "text": "Additionally, researchers should include in propensity score models all variables that might relate to the outcome even if they are unrelated to assignment, which also was the recommendation of [CITATION_1] . In reality, nearly all pretreatment variables will have some relationship to both outcome and assignment, and researchers must adjust for that bias.",
